this for me! Wunderbar!

235
00:14:18,732 --> 00:14:21,302
[Ichika]
Charl and Laura are both absent
as well?

236
00:14:21,402 --> 00:14:23,504
Do you think there's
something going around?

237
00:14:23,604 --> 00:14:28,109
I'm not sure, but I do know that
Laura went to bed terribly early
yesterday evening.

238
00:14:28,209 --> 00:14:31,545
[Ichika]
Now that I think about it, when
I went by to check on Houki
yesterday,

239
00:14:31,645 --> 00:14:35,016
she would only tell me she was
okay from behind the door.

240
00:14:35,116 --> 00:14:38,252
[Cecilia]
I wonder if it could be because
of something she ate.

241
00:14:38,352 --> 00:14:41,455
Huh...? Cecilia.. did
you hurt you fingers?

242
00:14:41,555 --> 00:14:45,292
Huh...?! What..? Oh, this?
It's nothing to worry about!

243
00:14:45,392 --> 00:14:47,194
[Ichika] Oh...

244
00:14:47,294 --> 00:14:48,762
[Cecilia]
Um, by the way, Ichika!

245
00:14:48,862 --> 00:14:52,433
Would you.. like to join
me for lunch tomorrow?

246
00:14:52,533 --> 00:14:55,569
I shall prepare a picnic lunch
for us and bring it with me.

247
00:14:55,669 --> 00:15:01,475
What...? Well, umm...
I.. don't mind lunch

248
00:15:01,575 --> 00:15:04,078
(awkward laugh) Sure, we
can eat lunch together...

249
00:15:04,178 --> 00:15:09,550
Ohhh, hah, then I'll see you at
lunch tomorrow on the rooftop!

250
00:15:09,650 --> 00:15:12,286
[Ichika]
Uh, okay then...

251
00:15:12,386 --> 00:15:13,520
[Kanzashi]
Hi, Ichika...

252
00:15:13,620 --> 00:15:16,490
Hey, Kanzashi... How are you?

253
00:15:16,590 --> 00:15:20,327
Actually, I was, uh, cooking
and made too much for lunch...

254
00:15:20,427 --> 00:15:22,829
So... I was wondering if you'd
like to have some?

255
00:15:22,929 --> 00:15:24,498
(Cecilia gasp)

256
00:15:27,601 --> 00:15:29,170
Man, this is so cool!

257
00:15:29,270 --> 00:15:32,439
Her lunch box is a truly
magnificent work of art...!

258
00:15:32,539 --> 00:15:34,941
I will never be able to
compete against that!

259
00:15:35,042 --> 00:15:39,446
So. Are you saying that you want
me to teach you how to make
sweet and sour pork?

260
00:15:39,546 --> 00:15:42,183
Yes, I do, Rin. Truly!

261
00:15:42,283 --> 00:15:43,584
Are you kidding me?!

262
00:15:43,684 --> 00:15:45,686
[Rinin, thinking]
Cooking WITH Cecilia?!

263
00:15:45,786 --> 00:15:48,689
That has to be the most deadly
combination in the world!

264
00:15:48,789 --> 00:15:51,558
Please! Today's the only
time we can do it.

265
00:15:51,658 --> 00:15:53,860
But I really
don't want to die!

266
00:15:53,961 --> 00:15:55,829
Oh, please!

267
00:15:58,065 --> 00:16:01,735
Please help me, Rin! You're
the only one I can count on!

268
00:16:01,835 --> 00:16:05,772
[Rinin, thinking]
A long time ago, I was a pretty
bad cook myself,

269
00:16:05,872 --> 00:16:07,941
so I'd like
to help her out, but then...

270
00:16:08,042 --> 00:16:14,015
Oh, no way! She's a deadly
weapon! One tiny slip could
be a fatal mistake!

271
00:16:14,115 --> 00:16:15,882
(Gasp) Hold on...

272
00:16:15,983 --> 00:16:17,884
[Rinin]
What's wrong with your fingers?

273
00:16:17,985 --> 00:16:20,421
(Gasp) Oh, this..
happened..

274
00:16:20,521 --> 00:16:22,556
when I was practicing
cutting with a knife...

275
00:16:22,656 --> 00:16:25,859
But... It's really not
a big deal at all.

276
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:27,928
Mm...

277
00:16:34,969 --> 00:16:38,605
All right then, I'll do it!
I'll teach you how to make
sweet and sour pork..!

278
00:16:38,705 --> 00:16:42,643
But remember, you have
to taste your own food!

279
00:16:42,743 --> 00:16:44,445
[Rinin]
So, now that we've
fried the pork,

280
00:16:44,545 --> 00:16:46,380
the next step will be to
sautÃ© the vegetables.

281
00:16:46,480 --> 00:16:48,182
You mean like this?

282
00:16:49,283 --> 00:16:51,485
Hey! It's looking good.

283
00:16:51,585 --> 00:16:53,420
This is when I would normally
crank up the heat

284
00:16:53,520 --> 00:16:55,522
until the flames came
leaping out, but...

285
00:16:55,622 --> 00:16:57,258
'Til the flames
are leaping out?!

286
00:16:57,358 --> 00:17:00,627
That's right. Chinese food
is all about firepower!

287
00:17:00,727 --> 00:17:03,697
[Rinin] Anyway, we can't have
flames with an electric stove...

288
00:17:03,797 --> 00:17:05,699
Let me handle that!

289
00:17:05,799 --> 00:17:06,900
Huh?

290
00:17:09,070 --> 00:17:11,738
[Rinin] Uh...! AAAHH!

291
00:17:24,976 --> 00:17:28,896
I'm sorry, Ichika... but I
wasn't able to prepare the
bentos for us last night
because,

292
00:17:28,996 --> 00:17:32,400
for some reason or other...
the food exploded...

293
00:17:32,500 --> 00:17:34,469
Uh... exploded?

294
00:17:34,569 --> 00:17:36,337
I'm especially disappointed,

295
00:17:36,437 --> 00:17:40,108
because I was really looking
forward to watching you enjoy my
cooking, too...

296
00:17:42,377 --> 00:17:45,380
[Ichika]
Well why don't we go make
something together right
now, okay...?

297
00:17:45,480 --> 00:17:46,847
We don't have to buy our lunch.

298
00:17:46,947 --> 00:17:50,118
And I'll teach you how to
make... my favorite dish!

299
00:17:50,218 --> 00:17:52,220
Huh?

300
00:17:53,688 --> 00:17:56,091
[Ichika]
Cecilia... are you
ready for this?

301
00:17:56,191 --> 00:18:01,029
[Cecilia]
Uh, yes...! But I
am rather nervous.

302
00:18:02,397 --> 00:18:04,932
[Ichika]
Look, Cecilia... we
don't have to do this...

303
00:18:05,033 --> 00:18:06,734
if you don't feel comfortable.

304
00:18:06,834 --> 00:18:11,639
[Cecilia]
No, I can do this!
We're already here.

305
00:18:11,739 --> 00:18:13,108
[Cecilia]
I'll be fine.

306
00:18:13,208 --> 00:18:16,277
[Ichika]
Okay then. Now, take
it in both hands...

307
00:18:16,377 --> 00:18:18,012
and hold it gently...

308
00:18:18,113 --> 00:18:19,947
[Cecilia]
Gasp! It's so very warm.

309
00:18:20,048 --> 00:18:25,820
[Ichika]
Mhmmm... Then you wet it
thoroughly, like this...

310
00:18:25,920 --> 00:18:27,355
[Cecilia]
Mm‐hm. Like this...?

311
00:18:27,455 --> 00:18:33,761
[Ichika]
Yeah, I like that. All right
then, let's do it.

312
00:18:33,861 --> 00:18:37,065
[Cecilia]
Uh, okay.

313
00:18:38,433 --> 00:18:40,968
[Cecilia]
So... like this?

314
00:18:41,069 --> 00:18:44,772
[Ichika]
Uh‐huh. And now you
can pick your filling.

315
00:18:44,872 --> 00:18:47,408
[Cecilia]
What are those
red thingies there?

316
00:18:48,609 --> 00:18:52,413
Oh those? Those are
pickled plum... Try one.

317
00:18:52,513 --> 00:18:56,384
(Gasp) Chomp.
(reaction to sourness)

318
00:18:56,484 --> 00:18:58,653
[Ichika] (laughter)

319
00:18:58,753 --> 00:19:03,458
[Ichika]
Next, you press the rice into
