320
00:19:03,558 --> 00:19:04,992
[Cecilia]
Let's see. Is this right?

321
00:19:05,093 --> 00:19:08,129
[Ichika]
No, You have to squeeze
it a bit more gently.

322
00:19:11,899 --> 00:19:12,967
(Ichika chuckles)

323
00:19:13,068 --> 00:19:15,536
Hey! Were laughing
at me just then?!

324
00:19:15,636 --> 00:19:17,605
[Ichika] I'm sorry.

325
00:19:17,705 --> 00:19:19,074
[Ichika]
You were just... so cute.

326
00:19:19,174 --> 00:19:22,277
Ah? You thought that I was cute?

327
00:19:22,377 --> 00:19:24,812
That's hard to believe.

328
00:19:24,912 --> 00:19:27,115
[Ichika]
Hey, let's try something?

329
00:19:28,283 --> 00:19:29,717
(Cecilia gasps)

330
00:19:30,885 --> 00:19:33,921
So.. The key is to squeeze
it in firmly and tight.

331
00:19:34,989 --> 00:19:37,725
[Cecilia] Uh‐huh...

332
00:19:37,825 --> 00:19:39,260
[Ichika]
There! Now it's done.

333
00:19:39,360 --> 00:19:42,497
